data.description: Well-maintained home with loads of woodwork, charm, and updates. Spacious front porch. Large living room with a brick wood-burning fireplace surrounded by built-in bookshelves with glass doors. The spacious dining room is perfect for large gatherings around the table, featuring a window seat for storage, and original hardwood floors. An updated kitchen with new appliances that are negotiable. From the kitchen step out the back door to the large deck and fenced-in backyard. Updates include vinyl windows, an electric breaker box, and a shingle roof (August 2022). Terrific two-car detached garage. The rear yard is fenced and adjoins Aljancic City Park with pickleball courts, tennis courts, a walking trail, and a large playground. VA loan assumption at a great rate is available for qualified buyers.
